{"tid":1043784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"理大學生紀律委員會教畜名單","createTime":"2019-03-02T13:36:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T09:46:59.000Z","uid":129134,"like":103,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"edf0cac778574f58204f52f41ea1682dd5af60d9","tid":1043784,"uid":129134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T13:36:38.000Z","msg":"主席 <strong>陳紹禮 土木及結構工程學系教授</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.polyu.edu.hk/cee/images/article/people/academic/06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.polyu.edu.hk%2Fcee%2Fimages%2Farticle%2Fpeople%2Facademic%2F06.jpg&h=9c2dae57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成員 <strong>莫志明 理大學務長／教授測量師</strong><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.lsgi.polyu.edu.hk/_images/people/academic/mok-chi-ming.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lsgi.polyu.edu.hk%2F_images%2Fpeople%2Facademic%2Fmok-chi-ming.jpg&h=390a237c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1）理大學務長莫志明要求理大學生會在24小時內把民主牆恢復原狀，否則將沒收民主牆<br />\n2）及後<span style=\"color: red;\">民主牆遭學校保安用中國國旗覆蓋</span><br />\n3）理大學生會前往高層辦公室理論，理大學務長莫志明在混亂中插水，學生上前扶起，莫志明指「會原諒學生整親佢隻腳」<br />\n<br />\n原本民主牆<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/211207_b2919b936a302d445426e2dcc631f702.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F211207_b2919b936a302d445426e2dcc631f702.png&h=a2af3b62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n後來民主牆（網上圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/211205_7de4b56e5e760b7c1cf7c8baa609fa8d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F211205_7de4b56e5e760b7c1cf7c8baa609fa8d.jpg&h=b79d0361&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/211203_6ac8fb69624e0c3ff719f2784f1dffb1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F211203_6ac8fb69624e0c3ff719f2784f1dffb1.jpg&h=e3d1ee62&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/211204_5ca9b91400d5f2190aa1dff18c506556.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F211204_5ca9b91400d5f2190aa1dff18c506556.jpg&h=1244e70b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n［我會原諒你事件］（網上圖片及文字）<br />\n混亂中，教授突然單腳跌在地上，何同學即時上前扶起，緊張地問：「你有無事？有無事？需唔需要搵個地方坐低？」<br />\n<br />\n教授猶豫了一陣，表示沒事，並用手搭著何同學膊頭，連聲表示「我會原諒你」、「我會原諒你」，何同學卻向對方說：「我唔係要你原諒我，我係唔會原諒校方打壓民主自由！」<br />\n<br />\n教授隨即澄清：「我係話我會原諒你整親我隻腳」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/211443_00fb7f2091cff6afb826ded61cd6049a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F211443_00fb7f2091cff6afb826ded61cd6049a.jpg&h=ad91b3c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n理大學生紀律委員會指控涉事學生4項罪名，包括出言譴責時任暫任副校長（學生）沈岐平和學務長莫志明，「你哋收共產黨錢收得咁過癮，舐共舐得你哋咁開心呀啦，屎忽鬼」，被指誹謗成立。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/212636_abf50fe0959ef12424c987aa1cc66aa9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F212636_abf50fe0959ef12424c987aa1cc66aa9.png&h=44eefea9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成員 <strong>黃永德 應用科學及紡織學院院長</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.sustc.edu.cn/upload/images/news/zonghexinwen/DSC_0226.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sustc.edu.cn%2Fupload%2Fimages%2Fnews%2Fzonghexinwen%2FDSC_0226.jpg&h=7823d84a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成員 <strong>陳炳泉 建築及房地產學系教授</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.polyu.edu.hk/web/filemanager/polyumainmediarelease/en/upload/2308/20120531202202_IMG_2_resize.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.polyu.edu.hk%2Fweb%2Ffilemanager%2Fpolyumainmediarelease%2Fen%2Fupload%2F2308%2F20120531202202_IMG_2_resize.JPG&h=b95da652&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成員 <strong>Prof. Yu Wing-yiu, Michael 應用生物及化學科技學系</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.polyu.edu.hk/abct/filemanager/staff/common/upload/23/34/Dr-YuWingYiu-Michael.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.polyu.edu.hk%2Fabct%2Ffilemanager%2Fstaff%2Fcommon%2Fupload%2F23%2F34%2FDr-YuWingYiu-Michael.jpg&h=0193601e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成員 <strong>陳振沖 電算機學系教授</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.comp.polyu.edu.hk/files/staff-profile-picture-chan-keith.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.comp.polyu.edu.hk%2Ffiles%2Fstaff-profile-picture-chan-keith.jpg&h=463b46c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成員 <strong>Dr Allen Ming-Yan Cheong</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.rgstatic.net/ii/profile.image/518845250183169-1500713755327_Q512/Allen_Cheong.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.rgstatic.net%2Fii%2Fprofile.image%2F518845250183169-1500713755327_Q512%2FAllen_Cheong.jpg&h=f00abdd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成員 <strong>何兆鎏教授 協理副校長（學術支援）</strong><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.ee.polyu.edu.hk/images/people/1461814327vI68X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ee.polyu.edu.hk%2Fimages%2Fpeople%2F1461814327vI68X.jpg&h=4003bff0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同場加映 <strong>時任理大大學校長 第十二屆、第十三屆全國政協委員 唐偉章</strong><br />\n著名中聯辦組織香港青年大專學生協會 及 香港新一代文化協會 榮譽顧問<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.newgen.org.hk/wp-content/uploads/bfi_thumb/20101030135533i-nkla51vxtapzkdrbqcxni2ja4o0yqmr51eao0rdybw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.newgen.org.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fbfi_thumb%2F20101030135533i-nkla51vxtapzkdrbqcxni2ja4o0yqmr51eao0rdybw.jpg&h=e02d45ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n理工大學去年10月初發生民主牆風波，理大學生紀律委員會昨日召開聆訊後，分別勒令4人退學、停學或須履行社會服務令。<span style=\"color: red;\">理大前校長唐偉章表示，對前同事有信心，並指相信校方相關人員是經過謹慎考慮才作出決定，對裁決毫無疑問。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n理大學生紀律委員會教畜名單來源<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.polyu.edu.hk/ppoffice/CommitteePresident/c_discipline.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.polyu.edu.hk%2Fppoffice%2FCommitteePresident%2Fc_discipline.pdf&d=Xug72IqGonTeMs94ciZuWsyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=67a1b9f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.polyu.edu.hk/ppoffice/CommitteePresident/c_discipline.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"9dde20fc2c9c0589c7985558fad2af48f53c48aa","tid":1043784,"uid":117584,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T13:46:04.000Z","msg":"推一舊先"},{"pid":"1283e8bd7cf776fc95feef32cdc34ec4b55d717e","tid":1043784,"uid":117584,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T13:46:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推一推先</blockquote>"},{"pid":"141af35c0972b61993af271877c6f6c910aa4f8b","tid":1043784,"uid":129134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T13:53:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a6706d468335ad65bdb34512c422e88409887048","tid":1043784,"uid":130695,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T13:53:52.000Z","msg":"你哋收共產黨錢收得咁過癮，舐共舐得你哋咁開心呀啦，屎忽鬼"},{"pid":"76a3845c11cdc6d1eed9f66355a19bcc8f311022","tid":1043784,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T14:09:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"094acd93f8200d1d6759db3fb4912bc6e9793ab7","tid":1043784,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T14:22:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ce5e59e9a43eafdbb3efa61fd86da171389a95fe","tid":1043784,"uid":126510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T14:56:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eeacf76307b8bbb4d21919c42a7053ac45cfcfe","tid":1043784,"uid":200975,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T14:58:10.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4884189955e326b27c18db7fc11271a62b5fd900","tid":1043784,"uid":128763,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T15:19:35.000Z","msg":"為人師表？埋沒良知<br />\n淪落到做共匪既打手"},{"pid":"5c818cbf68118ad4e22ebb797db76d578a87f2d1","tid":1043784,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T16:08:35.000Z","msg":"成班都係仆街黎<br />\n<br />\n公民黨議員助理及社民連也是仆街"},{"pid":"ef23d74f084f1625ee3665d2b4e41a5756e74416","tid":1043784,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4884189955e326b27c18db7fc11271a62b5fd900","tid":1043784,"uid":128763,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T15:19:35.000Z","msg":"為人師表？埋沒良知<br />\n淪落到做共匪既打手"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T16:09:13.000Z","msg":"谷卓恒話有數萬名特工"},{"pid":"d0234e776021b79e98b6a34d77999d45554054ac","tid":1043784,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T16:27:55.000Z","msg":"共青長大後"},{"pid":"504b6bd87306003446bdc777f9bdbb06a8dd72cf","tid":1043784,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T16:33:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"34fde1d07fdde92196cde08ca709352d3af092a3","tid":1043784,"uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ef23d74f084f1625ee3665d2b4e41a5756e74416","tid":1043784,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4884189955e326b27c18db7fc11271a62b5fd900","tid":1043784,"uid":128763,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T15:19:35.000Z","msg":"為人師表？埋沒良知<br />\n淪落到做共匪既打手"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T16:09:13.000Z","msg":"谷卓恒話有數萬名特工"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T16:56:18.000Z","msg":"1） 調查既係其中五個委員加一個學生，邊五個先<br />\n同埋，做到哩啲位係遴選<br />\n香港有好多professor 外國番嚟，嗰啲好多都係較開放同錫學生既<br />\n<br />\n2）我見到個list,唯一個學生名就係前學生會長<br />\n咁實際上有冇學生代表參與委員會，定係得五個professor決定？"},{"pid":"58828007033b3f3e6e02ce0f0d1063ecef4c9576","tid":1043784,"uid":48083,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"rep